        <div class="mainpara">
            <p>
                Nestled in the quiet suburbs of Kadawatha, Sri Lanka, our home
                garden is a vibrant haven for a rich variety of bird species.
                From familiar visitors to seasonal migrants like the Indian
                Paradise Flycatcher, each adds its own unique charm to this
                peaceful neighbourhood. In 2025, we created our very first
                documentary, filming these birds up close and capturing their
                beauty without disturbing their daily lives. It was a journey
                filled with discovery, patience, and the joy of seeing wildlife
                thrive right at our doorstep.
            </p>
        </div>

